# project-brain pack ownership
#
# This file specifies ownership of critical project-brain files and directories.
# Teams adopting this pack in their own repository should REPLACE @project-brain-maintainers
# with their own team handle (e.g., @myteam/infrastructure). If you don't want CODEOWNERS
# coverage, you can delete this file entirely.
#

# Core pack definition and schema
/CONVENTIONS.md           @project-brain-maintainers
/README.md                @project-brain-maintainers
/CONTRIBUTING.md          @project-brain-maintainers
/SECURITY.md              @project-brain-maintainers
/LICENSE                  @project-brain-maintainers

# Validator and tooling
/scripts/                 @project-brain-maintainers

# Assets, templates, and personas
/assets/                  @project-brain-maintainers

# Individual skills
/skills/                  @project-brain-maintainers

# Workflows and CI configuration
/.github/                 @project-brain-maintainers
